Venusaur (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0002: Ivysaur
Pokémon
#0004: Charmander →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Venusaur (TCG Pocket).

Venusaur has been featured on 27 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Venusaur cards are normally Grass-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Venusaur

Venusaur
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
